data.title: I Bet
data.meta_description: Another joint off BH2 feat the Captain of Ty's new squad Taylor Gang
data.text:
Stream I Bet, the newest drop from Ty Dolla $ign which features Wiz Khalifa. The cut was released on Wednesday, July 3rd, 2013. Things are looking better for Ty Dolla $ign with each new release, which I Bet has proven yet again. It's worthy addition to the impressive body of work Ty Dolla $ign has been developing over the years. We're looking forward to hearing what's next.

Hear more of Ty Dolla $ign on Paranoid (Prod. By DJ Mustard), featuring B.o.B. If you're down, make sure to visit Ty Dolla $ign's profile page for the newest info, news, songs, and mixtapes. Follow Ty Dolla $ign on Facebook and Twitter, if you aren't already.
